This was like being a little kid and opening a box of candy you weren't meant to have! These were the types of films that my wife and mine's dads would sit up late to watch (and we would sneak peeks at here and there) so it was familiar looking ground, but we were treated to seeing the entire movies!! Seriously, not knowing where to start to explore the old 'classic porn' , we watched a Showtime documentary on the ten greatest porn movies and this whole pack was basically on that list-the other movie 'Broadcast News' I got to satisfy my curiosity. They were all good,  'Deep Throat' was the hottest sex scenes,  'Devil in Miss Jones' made me think with the plot along with the juicy sex, and the others were enjoyable just for the worlds they created. I mean, Ron Jeremy in a BDSM scene blew my mind, really.
But yes, this is well recommended to anyone familiar with or curious about the sex film of this era (circa early 70's)
